tion><![CDATA[<p>南丰集团可持续时尚和技术创新平台的投资组合公司<a href="https://www.scmp.com/business/companies/article/3139432/hong-kong-fashion-tech-incubator-looking-make-industry-green?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3221919_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="33b56eb6-d9b2-11eb-8921-c363d46ef7af" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">Mills Fabrica</a>与零售巨头 Zara 合作推出了一个使用回收纺织废料制成的服装系列。</p><p>该服装系列依赖于美国循环纺织公司 Circ 的一项技术，该技术将所谓的聚棉材料（将棉和聚酯混纺的织物）回收成可用于新衣服的分离聚酯和天然纤维素纤维。 </p><div class="meter__linear relative" id="default-meter-page-views-11"><img width="auto" height="1" src="https://www.scmp.com/images/1x1.png" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="dm__l3"><hr class="vertical-line"><div class="dm__lw"><svg class="dm__l" height="24" viewBox="0 0 18 24" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g style="stroke:#000;fill:none;fill-rule:evenodd;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:1.5"><rect height="13.5" rx="1.5" width="16.5" x=".75" y="9.75"></rect><path d="m3.75 9.75v-3.75c0-2.89949494 2.35050506-5.25 5.25-5.25 2.8994949 0 5.25 2.35050506 5.25 5.25v3.75"></path><path d="m9.00000067 15.75c-.20710745 0-.37500067.1678932-.37500067.3749993 0 .2071075.16789322.3750007.37500067.3750007.20710611 0 .37499933-.1678932.37499933-.3750007.0002665-.0995369-.03915673-.1950746-.10954072-.2654586-.070384-.070384-.16592164-.1098072-.26545861-.1095407z"></path></g></svg></div></div><div class="dm__b center-block"><div><div class="dm__h mb-16">您已达到免费文章数量限制。</div><div class="dm__t center-block">订阅 SCMP 以无限制地访问我们屡获殊荣的新闻</div><div class="dm__s2 mt-30"><div class="dm__sb" id="subscribe-btn-11-large" role="button" tabindex="0" subscriptions-action="subscribe" subscriptions-service="subscribe.google.com" subscriptions-display="true" subscriptions-decorate="">订阅</div><div class="dm__m"><span>或</span><a href="https://subscribe.scmp.com/">探索我们的计划</a></div></div></div><div subscriptions-actions="" subscriptions-display