hina/diplomacy/article/3186308/china-sends-food-aid-drought-stricken-horn-africa-accusations?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3221915_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="a1a2e8ae-6dbf-4075-b911-c09f94bd80f6" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">紧急粮食援助</a>，并将资助<a href="https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3206458/china-pledges-support-reconstruction-efforts-war-torn-ethiopia?utm_source=google_amp&amp;utm_medium=Off-Platform-referrals&amp;utm_campaign=3221915_inline_link" title="" data-entity-uuid="6370537d-4da0-40f7-8121-26ece26a5223" data-entity-type="node" data-entity-bundle="article">埃塞俄比亚在提格雷战争中遭到破坏的基础设施</a>重建。</p><p>秦在会见埃塞俄比亚副总理兼外交部长德梅克·梅科南·哈森时说，中国已经向该地区提供了两批粮食援助，并且“正在考虑提供新一批……以帮助各国缓解其迫切需求”。 </p><div class="meter__linear relative" id="default-meter-page-views-11"><img width="auto" height="1" src="https://www.scmp.com/images/1x1.png" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="dm__l3"><hr class="vertical-line"><div class="dm__lw"><svg class="dm__l" height="24" viewBox="0 0 18 24" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g style="stroke:#000;fill:none;fill-rule:evenodd;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:1.5"><rect height="13.5" rx="1.5" width="16.5" x=".75" y="9.75"></rect><path d="m3.75 9.75v-3.75c0-2.89949494 2.35050506-5.25 5.25-5.25 2.8994949 0 5.25 2.35050506 5.25 5.25v3.75"></path><path d="m9.00000067 15.75c-.20710745 0-.37500067.1678932-.37500067.3749993 0 .2071075.16789322.3750007.37500067.3750007.20710611 0 .37499933-.1678932.37499933-.3750007.0002665-.0995369-.03915673-.1950746-.10954072-.2654586-.070384-.070384-.16592164-.1098072-.26545861-.1095407z"></path></g></svg></div></div><div class="dm__b center-block"><div><div class="dm__h mb-16">您已达到免费文章数量限制。</div><div class="dm__t center-block">订阅 SCMP 以无限制地访问我们屡获殊荣的新闻</div><div class="dm__s2 mt-30"><div class="dm__sb" id="subscribe-btn-11-large" role="button" tabindex="0" subscriptions-action="sub